```
public Mono&lt;BigDecimal&gt; calculate(UUID id) {
    return repositoryB.findById(id)
            .zipWhen(b -&gt; serviceA.find(b.getId())
            .map(t -&gt; t.getT1().add(t.getT2()));
}
```

Also, please note, you can not add two `BigDecimals` with `+`.

